#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:1
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:4
msgid ""
"MagiAttention currently supports only <u>Hopper</u> and <u>Blackwell</u>. We"
" are actively working to support more GPU architectures in upcoming "
"releases."
msgstr ""
"MagiAttention 目前仅支持 <u>Hopper</u> 和 <u>Blackwell</u>。我们正在积极开发对更多 GPU "
"架构的支持，将在后续版本中推出。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:12
msgid "Setup Environment"
msgstr "设置环境"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:14
msgid "Activate an NGC-PyTorch Container"
msgstr "启动 NGC-PyTorch 容器"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:17
msgid ""
"We recommend you to use the standard [NGC-PyTorch Docker "
"Releases](https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/frameworks/pytorch-release-"
"notes/) for consistency of basic dependencies such as `Python`, `CUDA`, "
"`PyTorch`, etc."
msgstr ""
"我们建议您使用标准的 [NGC-PyTorch Docker "
"Releases](https://docs.nvidia.com/deeplearning/frameworks/pytorch-release-"
"notes/) 以保持 `Python`、`CUDA`、`PyTorch` 等基础依赖的一致性。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:21
msgid ""
"Due to performance issue caused by `CUDA-12`, we recommend you to use "
"`CUDA-13+` based NGC-PyTorch containers for optimal performance."
msgstr "由于 `CUDA-12` 导致的性能问题，我们建议您使用基于 `CUDA-13+` 的 NGC-PyTorch 容器以获得最佳性能。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:23
msgid ""
"And we add an assertion in the `setup.py` script to check the CUDA version "
"and abort the installation if the CUDA version is lower than `13.0`."
msgstr "我们在 `setup.py` 脚本中添加了断言来检查 CUDA 版本，如果 CUDA 版本低于 `13.0` 则会中止安装。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:25
msgid ""
"If you insist on using `CUDA-12` based containers, you can set the "
"environment variable `MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12=1`, but please "
"be aware that it may lead to significant performance degradation compared to"
" `CUDA-13+`."
msgstr ""
"如果您坚持使用基于 `CUDA-12` 的容器，可以设置环境变量 "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12=1`，但请注意这可能会导致与 `CUDA-13+` 相比显著的性能下降。"

