#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:61
msgid "Enable IBGDA (optional)"
msgstr "启用 IBGDA（可选）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:64
msgid ""
"If you would like to try using our [native group-collective "
"kernels](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/blog/native_grpcoll.html) when "
"`cp_size > 8` as the communication backend, i.e. a process group involving "
"both intranode (*connected through `NVLink`*) and internode (*visible "
"through `RDMA`*) peers, you're required to enable `IBGDA` on your bare-metal"
" host machine."
msgstr ""
"如果您想在 `cp_size > 8` 时使用我们的 [native group-collective kernels](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/blog/native_grpcoll.html) "
"作为通信后端，即涉及节点内（*通过 `NVLink` 连接*）和节点间（*通过 `RDMA` 可见*）的进程组，您需要在裸金属主机上启用 "
"`IBGDA`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:68
msgid ""
"This step needs to be performed on the **BARE-METAL HOST OPERATING SYSTEM**,"
" **NOT** inside a Docker or other containerized environment, as containers "
"do not manage the host kernel."
msgstr "此步骤需要在**裸金属主机操作系统**上执行，**不能**在 Docker 或其他容器化环境内执行，因为容器无法管理主机内核。"

