#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:88
msgid "Install flash_attn_cute (optional)"
msgstr "安装 flash_attn_cute（可选）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:91
msgid ""
"If you would like to try MagiAttention on Ampere or Blackwell, for now "
"you're required to install `flash_attn_cute` package to enable [FFA_FA "
"backend](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/blog/blackwell_ffa_fa4.html) as a "
"temporary workaround."
msgstr ""
"如果您想在 Ampere 或 Blackwell 上试用 MagiAttention，目前需要安装 `flash_attn_cute` 包以启用 "
"[FFA_FA backend](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/blog/blackwell_ffa_fa4.html) 作为临时解决方案。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:103
msgid "Install MagiAttention"
msgstr "安装 MagiAttention"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:105
msgid "Install MagiAttention From Source"
msgstr "从源码安装 MagiAttention"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:108
msgid ""
"This progress may take around 10~20 minutes and occupies `90%` of CPU "
"resources for the first time."
msgstr "此过程首次可能需要约 10~20 分钟，并占用 `90%` 的 CPU 资源。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:112
msgid ""
"We have several [environment variables](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/user_guide/env_variables.html#for-"
"build) to fine-grained control the installation progress, especially for "
"CUDA extension modules building."
msgstr ""
"我们提供了若干[环境变量](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/user_guide/env_variables.html#for-"
"build)来细粒度控制安装过程，尤其是 CUDA 扩展模块的构建。"

