msgid "pip install command for Hopper:"
msgstr "Hopper 的 pip install 命令："

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:121
msgid "pip install command for Blackwell:"
msgstr "Blackwell 的 pip install 命令："

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:130
msgid "pip install command for Ampere:"
msgstr "Ampere 的 pip install 命令："

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:140
msgid "PreCompile FFA_FA4 kernels (optional)"
msgstr "预编译 FFA_FA4 内核（可选）"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:143
msgid ""
"If you would like to try MagiAttention on Blackwell and you've already "
"installed both `magi_attention` and `flash_attn_cute` to enable [FFA_FA "
"backend](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/blog/blackwell_ffa_fa4.html), we "
"further recommend you to pre-compile the common cases for `FFA_FA4` kernels "
"before production usage to avoid runtime JIT re-compilation overhead, since "
"it is built upon [Cute "
"PythonDSL](https://docs.nvidia.com/cutlass/4.3.5/media/docs/pythonDSL/cute_dsl.html)."
msgstr ""
"如果您想在 Blackwell 上试用 MagiAttention，并且已经安装了 `magi_attention` 和 "
"`flash_attn_cute` 以启用 [FFA_FA backend](https://SandAI-"
"org.github.io/MagiAttention/docs/main/blog/blackwell_ffa_fa4.html)，我们进一步建议您在生产使用前预编译"
" `FFA_FA4` 内核的常见配置，以避免运行时 JIT 重新编译的开销，因为它基于 [Cute "
"PythonDSL](https://docs.nvidia.com/cutlass/4.3.5/media/docs/pythonDSL/cute_dsl.html)"
" 构建。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/install.md:145
msgid ""
"And the cache directory for pre-compiled kernels is "
"`/path/to/magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/` by default, which can be "
"overridden by setting the environment variable "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR` to specify a custom cache directory if "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"预编译内核的缓存目录默认为 `/path/to/magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`，如有需要，可通过设置环境变量 "
"`MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR` 来指定自定义缓存目录。"

